2. Complex JSON documents
=========================

when the JSON contains multiple nested struct or nested string fields it become complex.

Sample for nested struct fields
===============================
[
{
	"Country": "Australia",
	"User": {
		"name": {
			"first_name" : "Nanda",
			"middle_name" : "Kumar",
			"last_name" : "Govindan"
		},
		"address": {
			"unit":"8",
			"number": "39",
			"street": "Ross Street",
			"suburb" : "North Parramatta",
